The paper deals with computer vision tasks such as image classification and object detection, which suggests that it belongs to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of CNNs and their reconfiguration, which falls under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of pictorial language representation and visualization techniques also suggests that the paper may belong to the natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-category. Finally, the paper mentions the use of MS-COCO dataset, which is commonly used in multimedia (cs.MM) research.
